item.title: CVE-2023-20858|2023-02-21T00:00:00 -- n%2Fa -- vmware%20carbon%20black%20app%20control
item.description: VMware Carbon Black App Control 8.7.x prior to 8.7.8, 8.8.x prior to 8.8.6, and 8.9.x.prior to 8.9.4 contain an injection vulnerability. A malicious actor with privileged access to the App Control administration console may be able to use specially crafted input allowing access to the underlying server operating system.
